<plot>Ollie &amp; the Baked Halibut is about a Sea Otter that rescues a Halibut (fish) as it's being grilled up on the deck of a boat. The chef on boat, Sushi Sam, does not want to lose his lunch and goes crazy in his efforts to get the Halibut back. The little otter and the halibut are outmatched and out gunned. Can they? Will they? Whoa Nellie, it's Ollie!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?409960</url></doc>
